        <abstract>
            <p>Declines to undertake to have AM’s journal published but recommends possible publishers in England.</p>
            <p>Expresses scepticism about AM’s glacier theory. Emphasises role of floating ice instead. Mentions article by William Hopkins on movement of glaciers.</p>
        </abstract>
